snippet.title: Palpable | 3D claymation game | Trailer |
snippet.description:
Developing a machine to convert every frame of a claymation animation to 3D with photogrammetry wasn't easy. But we somehow did it and it has taken shape of a free little 3D platformer 


Link to the game and resources used: 

https://aerro.itch.io/palpable

https://sketchfab.com/adirandalen

some behind the scenes here https://twitter.com/adriangitsgud/status/1439182119146754053
